- Import Validator from `@repo/utils/validator` at the top
- Normalize to lowercase BEFORE validation
- Use `.length(3, Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER, ...)` for minimum length check
- Use `.regex(Slug.SLUG_REGEX, ...)` for pattern validation
- Preserve `ERROR_CODE` constant
- Preserve exact error messages

