- `docs/09-PATTERNS.md` — VO and Entity templates

## Why This Matters

Without this documentation:
- Engineers may create unnecessary VOs for simple enums/booleans (over-engineering)
- Engineers may use primitives without validation (violates domain invariants)
- Inconsistency in how properties are modeled across entities
